---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Classroom Clarity - AI Q&A" htmlClass="dark" bodyClass="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 font-display antialiased overflow-hidden h-screen flex">
<style>
  :root, .dark {
    --color-primary: #f4ab25;
    --color-background-dark: #121212;
    --color-surface-dark: #1e1e1e;
    --color-surface-darker: #181818;
    --color-accent-teal: #4db6ac;
  }
</style>
<aside class="w-[280px] flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col h-full bg-surface-darker border-r border-white/5">
<div class="p-6 pb-2">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<div class="bg-primary/20 p-2 rounded-lg text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">school</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<h1 class="text-white text-lg font-bold tracking-tight">Classroom Clarity</h1>
<p class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-normal">Student Edition</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<nav class="flex-1 px-4 py-6 flex flex-col gap-2 overflow-y-auto">
<button class="flex w-full cursor-pointer items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg h-10 px-4 bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors text-background-dark text-sm font-bold shadow-lg shadow-primary/10 mb-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">add</span>
<span>New Study Session</span>
</button>
<div class="space-y-1">
<p class="px-3 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 mt-2">Menu</p>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-white/5 text-white group hover:bg-white/10 transition-all" href="/">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-400 group-hover:text-primary">chat_bubble</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Current Chat</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 transition-all group" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:text-primary">history</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">History</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 transition-all group" href="/library">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:text-primary">folder_open</span>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Documents</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="mt-6 space-y-1">
<p class="px-3 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Recent</p>
<a class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 text-sm truncate transition-all" href="#">
                    AP Euro - French Revolution
                </a>
<a class="block px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 text-sm truncate transition-all" href="#">
                    Calculus - Derivatives
                </a>
</div>
</nav>
<div class="p-4 border-t border-white/5">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-2 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/5 cursor-pointer transition-colors">
<div class="h-9 w-9 rounded-full bg-cover bg-center ring-2 ring-white/10" data-alt="Portrait of a female student" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCMVSz6F2na1CcwozoIrYtMZRA3lYZskhqA_ubdtvhV8BErhXSWBbnULNvIF5yJlz3pzX0cFLPvc9TllxGyDevoCw_Rhs8JBMCaDMwKgiUnOUokWVo8fn4DYaA08GUztQRjVkanLqj_S7l0mOfeCcyS1LrmoOouUElMRLvJFAYbAbK6LsWw6UoJPez1v-12TMzkUnBJ2MPcPeBPKn1FafaZf87bqYVuG6QSU7D0irHUq4awGaSsH1FuKoE3_aT8AdOMlXCiHb9u5kWR')"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<p class="text-sm font-medium text-white">Sarah Jenkins</p>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Pro Plan</p>
</div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-500 ml-auto">settings</span>
</div>
</div>
</aside>
<main class="flex-1 flex flex-col h-full bg-background-dark relative">
<header class="h-16 flex items-center justify-between px-8 border-b border-white/5 bg-background-dark/80 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-20">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="flex items-center justify-center h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-accent-teal/10 text-accent-teal">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">menu_book</span>
</div>
<div>
<h2 class="text-white text-base font-bold leading-tight">AP European History</h2>
<p class="text-slate-400 text-xs">Chapter 4 • French Revolution Overview.pdf</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<button class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 text-xs font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">ios_share</span>
                    Export
                </button>
</div>
</header>
<div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-8 pb-32 scroll-smooth">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-6">
<div class="flex flex-col items-end gap-2 self-end max-w-[80%]">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
<span class="text-xs text-slate-400">You</span>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-dark border border-white/10 text-slate-100 px-5 py-4 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-sm shadow-sm">
<p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
                            What were the primary causes of the French Revolution according to this text?
                        </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 max-w-[90%] mt-2">
<div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-orange-900/20">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-[20px]">smart_toy</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 flex-1">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
<span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Classroom Clarity AI</span>
</div>
<div class="text-slate-200 text-base leading-7 space-y-4">
<p>Based on the uploaded document, the primary causes of the French Revolution were a combination of social inequality, economic hardship, and political ineptitude.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full bg-gradient-to-t from-background-dark via-background-dark to-transparent pt-10 pb-8 px-8 z-10">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
<div class="relative flex items-center group">
<div class="w-full bg-surface-dark border border-white/10 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl flex items-center p-2 pr-2 group-focus-within:border-primary/50 group-focus-within:ring-1 group-focus-within:ring-primary/50 transition-all">
<input class="flex-1 bg-transparent border-none text-white placeholder-slate-500 focus:ring-0 px-3 py-2 text-base h-12" placeholder="Ask a follow-up question..." type="text"/>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<button class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-background-dark rounded-xl transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg shadow-primary/20">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">arrow_upward</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
</Layout>
